@BFF_URL = https://bff-staging.example.com
@DATE = 2025-09-12

### Odoo: Create (or get) draft quote
POST {{BFF_URL}}/api/bff/odoo/quotes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientId": "c_demo",
  "market": "edomex",
  "notes": "smoke test",
  "meta": { "caseId": "case_demo" }
}

### Odoo: Add line to quote (replace Q-xxxx with quoteId from previous response)
POST {{BFF_URL}}/api/bff/odoo/quotes/Q-xxxx/lines
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Filtro de aceite",
  "oem": "A123-OF",
  "equivalent": "WIX-57045",
  "qty": 1,
  "unitPrice": 189,
  "currency": "MXN",
  "meta": { "caseId": "case_demo" }
}

### GNV: Station health (T+1)
GET {{BFF_URL}}/api/bff/gnv/stations/health?date={{DATE}}

### GNV: Template CSV
GET {{BFF_URL}}/api/bff/gnv/template.csv

### GNV: Guide PDF
GET {{BFF_URL}}/api/bff/gnv/guide.pdf

